{"tid":2422733,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"兩童無父母陪伴，抵美尋庇護，13年來首次","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T12:28:32.000Z","uid":211994,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e388334c2fbdd7316511d4dcad1107447180c60b","tid":2422733,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"英國內政部今日（25日）更新2020年第四季港人申請庇護的統計數字。根據資料，由去年10月至12月，共有21名港人到英國尋求政治庇護，數字比上一季的41宗下跌近一半，但當中包括<span class=\"gold\"><strong>2名「無人陪伴的尋求庇護兒童（UASC）」</strong></span>，即與父母或看護人分開，自行抵英尋求庇護的兒童或年輕人，是自2007年起，首次再有UASC申請個案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/J6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FJ6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=99f99163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210225%2FJ6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ%2F&h=b9274a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210225/J6BC3FVSVJE6LCPHRVFK7WZ2FQ/</a>"},{"pid":"640e748a9d799dfb2155361ea0e2c194e9fc24be","tid":2422733,"uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"大鑊，係唔係應該不推文，del post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd0dbcc3ab7a994bc4d2ece64b8a886938b62bd","tid":2422733,"uid":390108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:55:41.000Z","msg":"好想知佢地系幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455768cc3b73759898c352aae81b38cda42e031d","tid":2422733,"uid":98431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"要平安<br />\n<br />\n臭港唔留年青人 過多一兩代人會自弊"},{"pid":"d498588c4ad292c64c64a459bc88850d1b795b58","tid":2422733,"uid":341619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"即係抵英定抵美"},{"pid":"b7bc